---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Classic Car Clubs UK
description: Discover classic car clubs across the UK with contact details and more.
showBreadcrumb: false
---

<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">Classic Car Clubs Directory</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Discover classic car clubs across the UK, with contact details and more.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/club-directory/" class="button button-primary">Browse Directory</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="button button-secondary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="featured-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Featured Car Clubs</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Discover popular classic car clubs from across the UK</p>
    </div>

    <div class="club-grid">
      {% set featuredClubs = clubs | filter("featured") | limit(4) %}
      {% for club in featuredClubs %}
        {% include "components/club-card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
      <a href="/club-directory/" class="button button-primary">View All Clubs</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="featured-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Upcoming Events</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Classic car shows, meets, and events across the UK</p>
    </div>

    <div class="event-grid">
      {% set upcomingEvents = events | limit(3) %}
      {% for event in upcomingEvents %}
        {% include "components/event-card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
      <a href="/club-events/" class="button button-primary">View All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">About The Classic Car Clubs Directory</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          Welcome to the UK's premier directory of classic car clubs. Our mission is to connect enthusiasts with local and national clubs dedicated to preserving and celebrating classic automobiles.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're looking to join a club for your specific make or model, or simply want to connect with fellow classic car enthusiasts in your area, our comprehensive directory has you covered.
        </p>
        <p>
          From vintage British marques to American muscle, European sports cars to Japanese classics, you'll find clubs catering to every interest and era of motoring history.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="club-types-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Popular Car Club Types</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="club-types-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <div class="club-type-card" style="background-color: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h3>Jaguar Clubs</h3>
        <p>Clubs for Jaguar fans, from the E-Type to XJS, XK, and more.</p>
        <p><a href="/club-directory/?search=jaguar">View Clubs</a></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="club-type-card" style="background-color: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h3>Austin Clubs</h3>
        <p>For fans of Austin, Austin-Healey, and other British classics.</p>
        <p><a href="/club-directory/?search=austin">View Clubs</a></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="club-type-card" style="background-color: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h3>MG Clubs</h3>
        <p>From MGA to MGB, Midget, and all other MG models.</p>
        <p><a href="/club-directory/?search=mg">View Clubs</a></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="club-type-card" style="background-color: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h3>Triumph Clubs</h3>
        <p>Classic Triumph TR3, TR4, TR6, Spitfire, and more.</p>
        <p><a href="/club-directory/?search=triumph">View Clubs</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
